source:
TEXT_CMNDEFMATERIASLOT_00174_MUTAMIX_000_000Pshhh... Shkohhh...
Uplander is asking Mutamix to shifty-make? Uplander should be hand-swapping five pieces of need-not materia with Mutamix.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFMATERIASLOT_00174_MUTAMIX_000_000シュコォ……シュコォ……
ほいでは　合成　ためすぞな～？
5つの　マテリア　渡すぞな～！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFMATERIASLOT_00174_MUTAMIX_000_020<tab>Mixy-melt, melty-mix, squash and squeeze, squeeze and squash...
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFMATERIASLOT_00174_MUTAMIX_000_020かがやく　マテリア　集めて混ぜりゃ
新たな　マテリア　生まれるぞ～！
なにいろ　どのいろ　楽しみぞ～！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFMATERIASLOT_00174_MUTAMIX_000_030<tab>Bigeyes! Five need-not are reborn as one!
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFMATERIASLOT_00174_MUTAMIX_000_030ほいほい　合成完了ぞ～！
新たな　マテリア　生まれたぞ～！
TEXT_CMNDEFMATERIASLOT_00174_MUTAMIX_000_035<tab>こいつは　おどろき　大当たり～！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFMATERIASLOT_00174_MUTAMIX_000_040<tab>Materia reborn glows with much brightshine. For uplander, this is happy-day!
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFMATERIASLOT_00174_MUTAMIX_000_040ぴかぴか　つるつる　大成功～！
新たな　マテリア　生まれたぞ～！
強いかがやき　見事ぞな～！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFMATERIASLOT_00174_MUTAMIX_000_050<tab>Shifty-making is exciting chance-game, yes? Even Mutamix has no knowings of what reborn materia will be! Does uplander's heart not be all flutterdance?
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFMATERIASLOT_00174_MUTAMIX_000_050マテリア合成　不思議な合成
なにができるか　運しだい～！
いどむも勇気　やめるも勇気～！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFMATERIASLOT_00174_MUTAMIX_000_070<tab>Shkohhh? Uplanderbag is clutterfull! Mutamix cannot shifty-make if uplander cannot carry materia reborn!
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFMATERIASLOT_00174_MUTAMIX_000_070こいつは　残念　お断り～！
おぬしの　鞄は　もうパンパン～！
整理整頓　必要ぞ～！
